::Shredder::

Shredder stops in his tracks, looking down at his scanners. Two more Maximals 
had joined the Maximals he had been heading for. Two might have been allright 
for him, but four was probably too hard to handle.

Shredder turns around, looking for any sign of one of the Predacons that he 
had seen. He found none. He frowns. Something was not right...

Shredder walks back toward where he had left Lobstruck, once again readying 
his guns.
